name: Techtodo
body:
Just a simple App for a todo list.  Based on Ray Wenderlich's excellent ideas and tutorials.  Part of a learning and training exercise in cross platform App development.  

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
The Author, Jonathan Howell.  Based on an idea by Ray Wenderlich.

### Support or Contact
All support issues to Jonathan Howell.
